    <briefdescription>
<para>Integral constant type trait helper. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides a compile-time constant value of type bool. Used as a base class for other type traits that need to expose a boolean value.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Value</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The boolean value </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Type</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The type of the value (default: bool)</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
@SINCE_2_5.11 </para>
